<EmailTemplate name="SERI - Notify Transfer">
  <Description>
      *******************************************************************************
      *   This is the advanced Email Template for the Help Desk Notification flow.
      *
      *   To tie this into the Help Desk Executor flow, add the name of the 
      *   Email Template to the Configuration Object, "POC Configuration Data" in
      *   the attribute called "helpDesk-EmailTemplate".
      *******************************************************************************
  </Description>
  <Body>
    <![CDATA[
    <html>
      <img src="http://localhost:8080/identityiq/images/CustHeader.gif" width="480" height="75" alt="IdentityIQ" />
      <br><br>
      A transfer event has occured for user, <b>$firstName $lastName</b>.  Per corporate policy, 
      <b>$firstName $lastName</b> will be allowed to keep his/her old assignments for 28 days. 
      When the 28 days expire, the following roles and entitlements will be sunset.   If you 
      have a problem with this contact your friendly Security Officer.  <br>
      <br>
      <b><u>User Profile Details</u></b><br>
      <UL>
        <LI>Full Name: $firstName $lastName<br>
        <LI>Employee ID: $userId<br>
        <LI>Application: $application<br>
      </UL>
      <br> 

      #foreach ($acctReq in $ProvisioningPlan.getAccountRequests())
      <b><u>Application: $acctReq.getApplication().  Account ID: $acctReq.getNativeIdentity()</u></b>
      
      #foreach ($attrReq in $acctReq.getAttributeRequests())
      <UL>
        <LI>Operation: $attrReq.getOperation()<br>
        <LI>Attribute: $attrReq.getName()<br>
        <LI>Value(s): $attrReq.getValue()<br>
        #if ($attrReq.getRemoveDate())
        <LI>Sunset Date: $attrReq.getRemoveDate()<br>
		#end
      </UL>
      #end
      #end
      <br>
      Regards,<br>
      The IdentityIQ Administration Team<br>

      <center>
         <img src="http://localhost:8080/identityiq/images/IdentityIQLogo.png" alt="SailPoint IdentityIQ"/>
      </center>
    </html>
    ]]>
  </Body>
  <Subject>IdentityIQ Transfer Notice For $firstName $lastName - Help Desk Notification </Subject>
</EmailTemplate>




